      "rationale": "Testing performed under a single ASTM F1717 static compression-bending configuration only. Dynamic fatigue and torsional loading conditions not included in this validation activity. Required level 3 not achieved; achieved level 2 reflects single standardized test condition. This gap is acknowledged and scope of model use is correspondingly limited to static compression-bending prediction."
